__ Cantrip: Wilt ______________________________ Cost: 10 _____________________

Use:  cantrip wilt < optional target >          Material Component: flower
Use:  C wilt < optional target >

The cantrip wilt is a minor magic of the sphere of necromancy.  When used,
the caster will cause all flowers/roses/plants on the target/in the area
to wilt away into nothingness.  A good cantrip for those who don't have any
green fingers to speak of.
